content:
Add an OmniScript to a Lightning or Experience Cloud Page.

Add an OmniScript by adding the generated Lightning web component. The component is generated when you activate the OmniScript.

Deploy an OmniScript to make it available in Experience and Lightning App Builders.

Review options for launching an OmniScript from a Lightning or Experience Page, then:

* Add Your OmniScript to a Lightning Page
* Add Your OmniScript to Experience CloudPages

Embed FlexCards in an OmniScript.
title: Adding OmniScripts to Lightning and Experience Pages
